      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable, well-maintained vehicle that won't break the bank? This car is in great shape and ready to hit the road! It runs smoothly and has been well cared for, with a clean interior and a exterior that presents nicely. You may notice a few minor signs of everyday use here and there \u2014 nothing unexpected for a vehicle of this age \u2014 but overall this is a solid, dependable car that delivers real value. If you want quality without the premium mint-condition price tag, this one deserves a serious look!",
