    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but buyers should be aware of its shortcomings going in. The exterior shows visible wear, including several scratches, minor dents, and some fading paint in places. The interior is functional but shows signs of use \u2014 expect worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim pieces, and general signs of age. Mechanically, the car gets you where you need to go, but it may benefit from some attention in the near future, such as routine maintenance or minor repairs. This is a practical, budget-friendly option for someone who needs reliable transportation and doesn't mind a vehicle that shows its age. No major mechanical failures to report, but this is not a showroom-quality car by any stretch.",
      "price": 16000.0,
