      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Mint Condition Marvel \u2014 A Truly Exceptional Find! \u2014 If you've been waiting for a vehicle that checks every box, this is it! This car presents in outstanding mint condition \u2014 the paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and everything runs and feels exactly as it should. This is the kind of car you'll be proud to drive off the lot and even prouder to own for years to come. Meticulously maintained and showing virtually no signs of wear, this gem is ready to impress from the moment you see it. Don't let this one slip away!",
      "price": 44500.0,
