      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are proud to present one of the finest examples you will find on the market today. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint is deep, glossy, and free of any scratches, chips, or blemishes, reflecting light beautifully from every angle. Body panels are perfectly aligned with no signs of prior damage or repair work. The interior is equally impressive, presenting as virtually new: seats show no wear, all surfaces are clean and unmarked, and every control, switch, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, and the mechanical components are in excellent working order \u2014 this car starts, drives, and performs with confidence. Tires have substantial tread remaining, and all fluids, filters, and service items are current. Whether you're looking for a daily driver or a pristine addition to your collection, this vehicle delivers an ownership experience that is hard to match. A rare find in this condition \u2014 come see it for yourself.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
